snippet.title: Pig Eat Ball announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Eat, Fight, Solve, and Barf your way through hundreds of action-packed levels in the colossal, story-filled world of Pig Eat Ball!
Coming in 2018 http://www.pigeatball.com to Computers and Consoles.


Check what gets barfed up at:
• http://facebook.com/PigEatBall
• http://facebook.com/MommysBestGames
• http://twitter.com/MommysBestGames

Sweet trailer tune: "Struggle Sandwich" by Azureflux
http://freemusicarchive.org/music/Azureflux/Pocket_Boy/03_azureflux_-_struggle_sandwich
